<item>
            <title>[LU-18498] change HSM locking for llog operations</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18498</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;HSM using cdt-&amp;gt;cdt_lock semaphore, for llog processing, at ctd_llog_process(). Oppositely, llog using internal locking mechanism to prevent reading/writing concurrent access. It looks like HSM upper locking is useless. Let&apos;s improve this part.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
